{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3fe8e3973a","title":"解学恭和南开大学卫东总部座谈时传达陈伯达的指示","origin":"1967年11月13日清华大学井冈山斗批改战团编印《学习资料》第41期。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ec938e7344","index":0,"year":1967,"month":11,"day":null,"articleId":"3fe8e3973a"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"5f7ec2008c","name":"解学恭","type":"人物"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"},{"id":"c2ea24d42d","name":"解学恭"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2ee8a2ba99","type":"title","text":"解学恭和南开大学卫东总部座谈时传达陈伯达的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3fe8e3973a"},{"id":"686a20e759","type":"authors","text":"解学恭陈伯达","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3fe8e3973a"},{"id":"2d19c4db2a","type":"paragraph","text":"这次见了伯达同志，伯达同志指定三个人抓一抓，要让他们调查一下，要得很急，一个月交卷。伯达同志说：要很快抓，火烧眉毛了。要先作调查，大致有五个方面：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3fe8e3973a"},{"id":"8f4ff18278","type":"paragraph","text":"1、资产阶级如何在学校统治，如何腐蚀青年。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3fe8e3973a"},{"id":"d6f04ef0d2","type":"paragraph","text":"2、调查学制，从小学到大学多少年好。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3fe8e3973a"},{"id":"c66bacbe77","type":"paragraph","text":"3、教学内容如何编，那些去掉，那些保留，那些要精减，那些充实新内容。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3fe8e3973a"},{"id":"a4ca3bb904","type":"paragraph","text":"4、教学方法如何搞，可不可以自学为主，大家进行辩论。最多别人辅导一下。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3fe8e3973a"},{"id":"c9c0cb404c","type":"paragraph","text":"5、学校管理问题","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3fe8e3973a"},{"id":"fb87614eaa","type":"paragraph","text":"根据这个调查三个大学，三个中学、三个小学，在城市，在农村。调查研究的方法照毛主席调查研究方法，五六个人，七、八个人开调查会，有问有答。有原始记录，再整理，调查范围：教师、家长、高年级学生，要第一把手。这个调查任务希望你们很好地承担起来。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3fe8e3973a"},{"id":"ca472a5dd2","type":"appellation","text":"","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3fe8e3973a"}],"page":{"id":"7aae930fb2","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3fe8e3973a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}